Package com.common

Interface DispatcherInt

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
Dispatcher
public interface DispatcherInt extends Remote
The remote interface for Dispatcher objects. Specifies the methods that can be invoked remotely on a Dispatcher object.
